<div class="container mt-5">
    <h1>About Us</h1>
    <p class="lead">
        Welcome to the Pet Adoption Registration System, the all-in-one solution designed to support staff in managing pet adoptions efficiently and effectively. We provide the tools you need to focus on what truly matters—helping pets find loving homes.
    </p>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <p>
            The Pet Adoption Registration System was created with a clear mission: to simplify the adoption process for shelter staff while ensuring that every pet receives the best chance at finding their forever family. We understand the challenges that shelters face daily, from managing extensive pet records to coordinating adoption events and communicating with potential adopters. This platform was built to address those challenges and transform the way adoptions are managed.
        </p>
        <p>
            By streamlining administrative tasks and reducing manual effort, the system empowers your team to dedicate more time and energy to caring for the animals and building meaningful connections with adopters.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
        <p>
            Our platform isn’t just another software—it’s a partner in your mission. Here's what sets us apart:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Ease of Use:</strong> Intuitive interfaces and straightforward processes make the system accessible for everyone on your team.</li>
            <li><strong>Comprehensive Features:</strong> From pet profile management, user management, adoption tracking and reporting, we cover every aspect of your workflow.</li>
            <li><strong>Custom Solutions:</strong> Tailored to the unique needs of shelters, ensuring our tools align perfectly with your goals.</li>
            <li><strong>Support & Security:</strong> Robust security features protect sensitive information, while our support team is always ready to assist.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
            At the heart of the Pet Adoption Registration System lies a deep commitment to animals and the incredible individuals who care for them. Our mission is to:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Empower shelters and rescue organizations with modern tools.</li>
            <li>Reduce the administrative burden of managing adoptions.</li>
            <li>Help more pets find their forever homes by improving operational efficiency.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
            We believe that every pet deserves a second chance and every shelter deserves the support it needs to make that happen. Together, we can create a brighter future for animals everywhere.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Features Overview</h2>
        <p>
            The Pet Adoption Registration System offers a wide range of features designed to optimize every step of the adoption process:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Database:</strong> Maintain detailed profiles for every pet, user, and adoption record.</li>
            <li><strong>Adoption Workflow:</strong> Track each pet’s journey from shelter to their new home with real-time updates.</li>
            <li><strong>Reporting Tools:</strong> Generate insights and reports to measure your shelter's impact.</li>
            
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Looking Ahead</h2>
        <p>
            As we continue to develop and expand the Pet Adoption Registration System, we remain committed to supporting shelters in their vital work. Our goal is to create solutions that not only meet your current needs but also grow with you as you make an even greater impact in the future.
        </p>
        <p>
